    - Convert to debhelper for systemd init script installation
      (Closes: #889541)

  * debian/squid.{postinst,postrm}
    - Remove update-rc.d commands now done by debhelper

  * debian/NEWS.debian
    - Document surprises caused by systemd use (Closes: #896125)

